jabbot (0.4) unstable; urgency=medium
  
  [ Vincent Morsiani ] 
  * added multi body part support for jabbot messageContent
  * added body part validation mechanism 
  * private messaging support
  * messageContent interface refactoring
  * refactored commands to abstract it as extension
  * Added cicso Spark support (https://www.ciscospark.com/)
  * Added Slack support (https://slack.com/)
  * each jabbot module can now be built as a debian package
  * Resource mechanism to address messages to a Room or a User
  * jabbot-messaging-api : extracted common classes to a separate module
  * Binding Monitoring: core now detect when a binding is disconnected and reconnects it.
  * Xmpp Binding now validate XHTML prior to send a message.
  * Switched communication between core & binding to an asynchronous event mechanism

 -- Vincent Morsiani <vmorsiani@gmail.com>  Thu, 23 Jun 2016 14:41:46 +0200

